snippet.title: Kickerinho LAUNCH TRAILER [iOS/Android/WP8]
snippet.description:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kickerinho

Apple AppStore: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id895557340

Google Play https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tabascointeractive.kickerinho

Amazon http://www.amazon.com/Tabasco-Interactive-Kickerinho/dp/B00M70ITRM

http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/kickerinho/991d10f9-8f5d-4240-af53-176dda71488e

Kickerinho needs your help to become best juggler in the beautiful city of Rio de Janeiro! Will you help him fulfill this dream?

Juggle with your foot and head! Stall the ball on your neck and show your friends who is better! But remember: juggling is a skill that is improved by repetition. The more you do the better you will get.
